<p source="SHANGBO.SHENZIYUEGONGJIAN 6.36.1 (STRIP 1) MACHENGYUAN 6: 276 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-1a.1">慎子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-1a.2">恭儉以立身,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-1a.3">堅強以立志,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-1a.4">忠質以返貞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-1a.5">逆友以載道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-1a.6">精法以巽藝.【1】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHENZIYUEGONGJIAN 6.36.2 (STRIP 2) MACHENGYUAN 6: 277 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-2a.1">[...]焉;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-2a.2">恭以為體,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-2a.3">道莫偏焉;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-2a.4">信以為言,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-2a.5">言莫偏焉;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-2a.6">強以賡志, [...][2]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHENZIYUEGONGJIAN 6.36.3 (STRIP 4) MACHENGYUAN 6: 279 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-3a.1">[...] 苟得用于世,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-3a.2">均分而廣施,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-3a.3">恃德而傍義.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-3a.4">民之[...] [4]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHENZIYUEGONGJIAN 6.36.4 (STRIP 3) MACHENGYUAN 6: 278 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-4a.1">[...] 物以丕(=奉)身,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-4a.2">中處而不頗,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-4a.3">任德以 [.],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-4a.4">故曰</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-4a.5">清斷 [...] [3]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHENZIYUEGONGJIAN 6.36.5 (STRIP 5) MACHENGYUAN 6: 276 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-5a.1">祿不累其志,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-5a.2">故曰强.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-5a.3">首戴茅蒲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-5a.4">撰蓧執鉏,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-5a.5">塍畎傭耕必于......[5]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHENZIYUEGONGJIAN 6.36.6 (STRIPS 6) MACHENGYUAN 6: 281 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-6a.1">踐今爲民之故,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-6a.2">仁之至.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-6a.3">是以君子向方知道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0065_tls_001-6a.4">不可以疑臨......[6]</seg></p>

